    <tags>cleansweep disk-cleanup cleaner disk-space free-space windows admin</tags>
    <summary>Free Windows tool to reclaim disk space (orphaned program leftovers, large files, caches, Windows.old and more).</summary>
    <description>
CleanSweep is a free, multilingual Windows tool that frees up disk space. It finds
orphaned program folders, large unused files, temporary files, browser and app
caches, Windows Update leftovers, Windows.old and more, and removes them safely
(to the Recycle Bin, reversible).

Features: dark mode, six languages (DE/EN/FR/ES/PL/UK), Beginner/Expert mode,
protection lists for system folders, "last used" detection to spare active apps.
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/acc328512-max/CleanSweep/releases/tag/v1.0</releaseNotes>
